Papersᵞ — Discussing board for scientific papers 
================================================

we use python3, flask, werkzeug, sqlite3, gs


Installation
------------

0. ./clear.sh will initialize sqlite database and pdf's storage

1. Copy papersite/config.py.example to papersite/config.py
 
2. Read, understand and modify papersite/config.py.
   Do not forget to change SALT1, SALT2 and mail-server's parameters.

3. Prepare (virtualenv... etc TODO)

3. ./run.sh

 